spanGrp.span: haya wazazeedeny qay anyaseewi aa gomew seen
Okay, my parents they have all passed away
Haya na wazazi wangu niliyowakuta wote wamekufa
In the old days even my grandmother...
Zamani hata bibi zangu si wame......
ee qay an qambab gil an digeesit
In the old days my father's sister's family, Digesita's family
Zamani ni akina shangazi akina Digesita
Also she told us the order of the Asimjeeg
gidab ar qay asees gelab ar someeg
That even us in the old days we came from Someega
Kwamba hata sisi zamani tulitokea Somega
In the old days we came from Someega, we did
genyaseew ar an jajiideeny ar an qamateny aa an baba
We met our elders and my mother's family and my father's family
Tukawakuta babu zetu na akina mama zetu na akina baba yetu
gidaba asimjeeg asees qay gelab someg
That we the Asimjeeg came from Someega
This is the source of me getting married
wasaseed upandeed qe gwargweedeny aa gomewa
The parents on the side of my husband have all died
Wazazi wa upande wa mume wangu wamefariki wote
seen qay samureed qay siruk gidab asinjeeg gelab somega
This is also the order that the Asimjeeg came from Someege
Pia hayo ni amri kwamba waasimjega walitokea Somega
aa qayiid ng'anyiin seen ng'ashani qayiid aa qanyaseew jeed asimjeeg
gidab asees asimjeeg qay gelab someeg
That us Asimjeeg came from Someega
siyang'ulay aa godulan gid qay adaqdaydi
I think that is what I know from the old days
